        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/81600056/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u81600056-3.jpg" alt="向呆总致敬" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36989453/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36989453/" class="">第八章 </a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/81600056/" class=" " title="向呆总致敬">向呆总致敬</a>
                (优秀不够，你是否无可替代)
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="36989453">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">   社会生活的高度可见性和可搜索性意味着，想法相同的人们现在拥有了找到对方，聚集起来并且互相合作的能力，而不受社会赞成与否的态度制约</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-01-15 09:13</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                   社会生活的高度可见性和可搜索性意味着，想法相同的人们现在拥有了找到对方，聚集起来并且互相合作的能力，而不受社会赞成与否的态度制约
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/36989453/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2016-01-15 09:13
